snippet.title: Fix-It Felix Jr. - Commodore 64 teaser
snippet.description:
Commodore 64 conversion of "the most popular 2D platform game ever made"


Fix-It Felix Jr. is a Charity project.
Download the game for free or support UNICEF with a donation
https://brokenbytes.itch.io/fix-it-felix-jr

Fix-It Felix Jr. Development team:
Antonio Savona: Code
Steven Day: Graphics
Saul Cross: Sound
